l llc “berkley” the private equity investment vehicle of wr berkley corporation ghf served as exclusive financial advisor to cic in the transaction cic has developed proprietary gamechanging supply chain technology and processes for the promotional products market that shorten delivery times reduce error rates and decrease logistics costs cic’s platform provides clients with a streamlined turnkey solution for the distribution of branded merchandise and the operation of incentive and uniform programs the cic team is extremely excited to partner with berkley in the next phase of the company’s growth brian abrams founder of cic commented “ghf ran a tightly orchestrated sale process that generated many options for cic’s owners and discovered the perfect cultural fit for our employees we enjoyed working with their team and appreciate their dedicated hard work and the results they delivered” pete munson managing director at cardinal equity partners added “ghf did a fantastic job for us executing the cic sale process from drafting the book preparing for management meetings and most importantly finding the best buyers for the business ghf proved themselves to be exceptional selling a businesses that we really like is a difficult process but knowing it has a good partner to help it with its next phase is comforting” the transaction represents another successful outcome for ghf’s consumer products team joe lavely managing director at ghf commented “while driving industryleading growth and profit margins cic management has maintained a strong corporate culture focused on exceeding its clients’ expectations it was a pleasure for us to represent the marquis name in the promotional products industry in a very successful sale process” about corporate imaging concepts llc founded in 996 cic provides branded promotional products and online company store portals for some of the country’s largest corporations cic’s gamechanging leif™ technology solution leads the industry in customer satisfaction through supply chain efficiencies the company’s commitment to technology advancements combined with a workforce dedicated to exceeding customer expectations has resulted in steady doubledigit growth along with industry recognition as a sales leader and one of the best places to work for more information visit wwwcorpimagingcom about greene holcomb fisher greene holcomb fisher with offices in minneapolis phoenix seattle and atlanta is an investment banking firm that specializes in mergers and acquisitions private placements and financial advisory services for the middle market at greene holcomb fisher experience from nationally prominent investment banks and leading law firms is blended with seniorlevel attention and entrepreneurial ingenuity to deliver creative services to high quality companies greene holcomb fisher investment bankers specialize in the consumer food  agribusiness healthcare industrial products  services business  education services technology and energy  infrastructure sectors greene holcomb fisher provides global reach through clairfield international for more information please visit wwwghfnet and wwwclairfieldcom print email share via email separate multiple email addresses with commas share send me a copy email preview to from subject look at this story on pe hub cardinal equity partners sells corporate imaging concepts to berkley capital berkley capital llc the private equity investment vehicle of wr berkley corporation bought corporate imaging concepts llc a portfolio company of cardinal equity partners cic provides supply chain technology for the promotional products market investment banking firm greene holcomb fisher served as financial advisor to cic continue reading on pe hub writes do you want exclusive news and analysis about private equity deals fundraising topquartile managers and more get your free trial to buyouts or subscribe now sign up to our newsletter receive updates from our pe hub wire and top stories of the wee